===Etymology 2===
Alteration from {{term|こうべうち|lang=ja}}, itself a compound of {{term|首||head|tr=kōbe|lang=ja}} + {{term|打ち||striking, hitting|tr=uchi|lang=ja}}.

====Noun====
{{ja-noun|こぶち}}

